OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FLarge swathes of Wales are now
OL,8,Fofficially in drought status after
OL,9,Fsuccessive heatwaves and record-low
OL,10,Friver levels.
OL,12,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) declared
OL,13,Fthat north Wales and Upper Severn are
OL,14,Fin drought on Thursday afternoon (23
OL,15,FJuly).
OL,17,FThe NRW also confirmed that all
OL,18,Fremaining catchments across south-west
OL,19,FWales have moved from normal to
OL,20,Fprolonged dry weather status.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
