OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FThe areas affected include:
OL,9,FIt comes after the country has faced
OL,10,Fsuccessive heatwaves, widespread
OL,11,Fwildfires and record-low river levels.
OL,13,FThis means all of Wales is now
OL,14,Fexperiencing either prolonged dry
OL,15,Fweather or drought conditions. The
OL,16,Fdecision follows continued hot, dry
OL,17,Fweather over recent weeks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FNRW revealed that July is now on track
OL,8,Fto become the driest on record in
OL,9,FWales for almost 190 years, if
OL,10,F'significant rainfall' does not arrive
OL,11,Fbefore the end of the month.
OL,13,FNorth Wales and the Upper Severn has
OL,14,Freceived less than 2% of the expected
OL,15,Frainfall for the month so far.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FNRW has reported that river flows
OL,8,Facross large parts of North Wales and
OL,9,Fthe Upper Severn are now
OL,10,F'exceptionally low for the time of
OL,11,Fyear', with some locations approaching
OL,12,Frecord lows.
OL,14,FIn many areas of North Wales, there
OL,15,Fhas been no heavy rainfall since 6
OL,16,FJuly.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
