FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FImpacts of the drought include the
OL,8,Fdrying of private water supplies in
OL,9,Fsome areas, farmers needing to seek
OL,10,Falternative livestock watering
OL,11,Fsupplies and supplementary feeding due
OL,12,Fto reduced grass growth.
OL,14,FWhile water companies report that
OL,15,Freservoir levels remain healthy
OL,16,Foverall, NRW is encouraging people to
OL,17,Fuse water wisely.
OL,19,FWhat is a drought?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FAccording to the National Drought
OL,8,FMitigation Centre, a drought is 'a
OL,9,Fprotracted period of deficient
OL,10,Fprecipitation resulting in extensive
OL,11,Fdamage to crops, and a consequential
OL,12,Floss of yield'.
OL,14,FDrought is declared by NRW when a
OL,15,Fcombination of indicators show a
OL,16,Fsignificant shortage of rainfall and
OL,17,Fwater availability, resulting in
OL,18,Fimpacts on rivers, groundwater,
OL,19,Fecosystems, agriculture and land
OL,20,Fmanagement.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FWales was last declared to be in
OL,8,Fdrought status in August 2025, which
OL,9,Fcovered the south east part of the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FWhile water companies report that
OL,13,Freservoir levels remain healthy
OL,14,Foverall, NRW is encouraging people to
OL,15,Fuse water wisely.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FRhian Thomas, Sustainable Water and
OL,8,FNature Manager at NRW, said: "We have
OL,9,Fseen rivers fall to exceptionally low
OL,10,Flevels, groundwater continuing to
OL,11,Fdecline, and increasing reports of
OL,12,Fenvironmental impacts affecting
OL,13,Fwildlife, fisheries, farming and
OL,14,Fsensitive habitats.
OL,16,F"The recent wildfires across North
OL,17,FWales and South East Wales are one of
OL,18,Fthe clearest and most visible signs of
OL,19,Fhow dry our landscapes have become.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784823525
OL,3,CDrought status for north Wales and
OL,4,CUpper Severn after record dry
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,F"Our teams continue to work closely
OL,8,Fwith fire and rescue services, local
OL,9,Fpartners and land managers to respond
OL,10,Fto these incidents and reduce risks
OL,11,Fwhere possible.
OL,13,F"While drought status does not
OL,14,Fautomatically mean water shortages for
OL,15,Fcustomers, we are asking everyone to
OL,16,Fplay their part by using water wisely
OL,17,Fand helping to protect Wales natural
OL,18,Fresources during this exceptionally
OL,19,Fdry period."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/9
